2005-10-03 Petri Damstén <petri.damsten@iki.fi>

  * Version 0.4.1 released
  * jumppad free dvdauthor.xml. Reported to work better with some dvd players.
  * Menu background audio support
  * Font selection for menus
  * Preview DVD in an internal DVD player
  * Play media files in an internal DVD player
  * Save template preview
  * Select menu for template preview
  * DVD info dialog
  * sox / toolame dependency removed
  * libdv, libxine and libdvdread are now optional dependencies.
  * Can add multiple video files at once now
  * Bug fixes

2005-08-16 Petri Damstén <petri.damsten@iki.fi>

  * Version 0.4.0 released
  * sox+mp2enc can be used instead of toolame
  * Aspect ratio fix to video preview
  * Layout engine fixes
  * New template 'Preview 1'
  * Configure dialog added
  * Option to play movie directly when disc inserted
    (Menu still available using remote)
  * Option to play movie directly in 'Preview 6'-template
    (without chapter menus)
  * Template specific configure dialogs
  * Better subtitle handling
  * Bug fixes

2005-06-15 Petri Damstén <petri.damsten@iki.fi>

  * Version 0.3.0 released
  * Import DV file and generate chapters and subtitles from timecodes.
  * Subtitle support
  * File format conversion
  * Travel and simple themes
  * i18n support for themes
  * aspect & audio language selection
  * Bug fixes

2005-04-19 Petri Damstén <petri.damsten@iki.fi>

  * Version 0.2.2 released
  * Chapter editor
  * Bug fixes

2005-04-11 Petri Damstén <petri.damsten@iki.fi>

  * Version 0.2.1 released
  * GUI fixes
  * K3b output

2005-03-28 Petri Damstén <petri.damsten@iki.fi>

  * Version 0.2.0 released
  * XML based template engine added

2005-01-28 Petri Damstén <petri.damsten@iki.fi>

  * Initial Release v 0.1.0
